ieve ads\"\",\"\"session\"\":\"\"e4b229a2-b0af-430f-aef0-a8814357ae26\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"warning\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-13T19:10:21.953188675Z\"\"}\",出现次数:1\n", "unique_entities": {"pod_name": ["frontend-1", "adservice-0", "frontend-0", "frontend-2"], "service_name": ["frontend", "adservice"], "node_name": ["aiops-k8s-07", "aiops-k8s-03", "aiops-k8s-04"]}, "matched_anomaly": "Please analyze the abnormal event between 2025-06-13T19:10:10Z and 2025-06-13T19:34:10Z and provide the root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-13 19:10:10+00:00 to 2025-06-13 19:34:10+00:00"}, "log_data_collected": true, "log_analysis_findings": "```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"context deadline exceeded\", \"AdService--gc\", \"java.lang.Exception\", \"InvocationTargetException\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"AdService experiencing garbage collection issues as seen from multiple GC-related logs.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"\\\"AdService--gc-1749841811 execute()\\\", \\\"org.jboss.byteman.agent.Transformer : inserted trigger for AdService--gc-1749841811 in class org.chaos_mesh.chaos_agent.TriggerThread\\\"\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"Frontend service unable to retrieve ads due to deadline exceeded errors.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"\\\"failed to get ads: rpc error: code = DeadlineExceeded desc = context deadline exceeded\\\"\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n#### Analysis\n- **Adservice**: The `adservice` seems to be undergoing stress related to garbage collection as indicated by logs containing references to `AdService--gc` and errors relating to Java exceptions.\n- **Frontend**: The `frontend` service is consistently reporting errors with retrieving ads due to `context deadline exceeded`, indicating potential delays or timeouts in connections to other services such as `adservice`. \n\nNo singular critical failure point is evident; rather, both services appear to have individual issues that might be mutually impacting each other, particularly the timeouts affecting frontend operations related to `adservice`. Further investigation could involve looking into resource constraints or improved handling of ads service request scheduling to alleviate deadline issues.", "metric_analysis_findings": "根据收集到的数据，我们可以进行如下分析：\n\n### 异常指标详解\n\n1. **Node 级故障**:\n   - **节点 `aiops-k8s-08`** 的 `node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes` 显著减少，变化率为 0.2638，可能引发内存相关问题。\n\n2. **Pod 级故障**:\n   - **Pod `adservice-2`** 的 `pod_cpu_usage` 变化率达到 2.0，虽然正常和故障时的中位数都为 0.0，但 P99 值有上升。\n   - **Pod `redis-cart-0`** 的 `pod_cpu_usage` P99 值显著上升，变化率为 0.3499。\n\n3. **Service 性能问题**:\n   - **`adservice`** 的 `rrt_max` 有显著增加，P99 变化率为 0.4325，表明响应时间高峰增大。\n   - **多个服务**(如 `shippingservice-1`, `currencyservice-1`)的 `rrt_max` 变化率较高，显示出响应时间有波动。\n\n4. **DB 级故障 (TiDB)**:\n   - `tidb-tikv` 的 `io_util` 指标变化率为 0.4339，显示出数据库 IO 使用率增高。\n\n### 异常实体根因分析\n\n#### Node 与 Pod 归因 - `aiops-k8s-08`\nPod `redis-cart-0` 在 `aiops-k8s-08` 节点上，其 `pod_cpu_usage` 显著变化，可能是引发节点内存问题的原因，需进一步排查该 Pod 的资源使用情况。\n\n#### TiDB IO 故障\n`tidb-tikv` 的 IO 使用率升高可能影响数据库性能，需关注 TiDB 组件的资源瓶颈而非其上游服务。\n\n### 输出 JSON格式\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"pod_cpu_usage\", \"rrt_max\", \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\", \"io_util\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"pod_cpu_usage 的 P99 有显著增长，可能导致 aiops-k8s-08 节点资源紧张\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_cpu_usage 的 P99 变化率为 0.3499\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"pod_cpu_usage 的 P99 增长且变化率为 2.0，可能影响其性能\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_cpu_usage 在故障期间显著异常\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"tidb-tikv\",\n      \"reason\": \"io_util 的 P99 变化率为 0.4339，显示数据库 IO 使用率增高\",\n      \"evidence\": \"io_util 在故障期间显著异常\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n此分析提供了多个潜在的根因与相关异常指标，为故障排查提供了进一步的导向。", "trace_analysis_findings": "根据给定的 Trace 数据，我将这一时间段内的异常调用链和延迟情况进行了初步分析。以下为我的发现：\n\n### 发现的异常调用链\n1. **显著延迟**\n   - `shippingservice` 在由 `checkoutservice` 调用时表现出明显延迟，特别是在 `hipstershop.ShippingService/ShipOrder` 操作上，其平均耗时从正常的 217ms 增加到异常时段的 1279ms。\n   - `checkoutservice` 自身在 `hipstershop.ShippingService/ShipOrder` 操作上表现出显著延迟，耗时从 13942ms 增加到 72859ms。\n   - `frontend` 在调用 `hipstershop.AdService/GetAds` 时，耗时显著增加，从 5431ms 增加到 33833ms。\n\n2. **错误传播**\n   - 多个 `frontend` pod在 `hipstershop.AdService/GetAds` 操作上回报了多次 `context deadline exceeded` 错误。\n\n### 延迟分析与根因\n- `checkoutservice` 调用 `shippingservice` 导致的延迟与错误链中同样存在对 `cartservice` 的影响，由 `checkoutservice` 发起的多次请求都伴随着显著的性能下降。\n- `redis` 在 `cartservice` 用 `HMSET` 命令时出现了显著延迟，特别是在 node `aiops-k8s-05` 和 `aiops-k8s-08` 上 (耗时从正常的 1655ms 增加到 33915ms，1361ms 增加到 25041ms)，可能是性能瓶颈之一。\n\n### JSON 输出\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\",\n    \"frontend->adservice\",\n    \"cartservice->redis\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"hipstershop.ShippingService/ShipOrder 操作在异常时段延迟增加 5 倍\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"hipstershop.AdService/GetAds 操作显著延迟，出现 context deadline exceeded 错误\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"cartservice 执行 HMSET 命令时延迟增加了超过 20 倍\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n根据这些发现，我们可以进一步深入分析系统的每个组件，特别是 `checkoutservice` 和与 `redis` 的交互来确定更深层的系统瓶颈及其根因。"}
